Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.51,0:00:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位，卡萊多之星開始了的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.41,0:00:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀看卡萊多之星的時候請保持室內的亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.02,0:00:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那麼，那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.32,0:00:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有沒有下過決心做某件事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.22,0:00:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這人生16年雖然發生了各種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.32,0:00:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受了各種挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.25,0:00:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可是認真、超級認真的下了決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.75,0:00:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了大家的明天！明天！明天！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.89,0:02:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見我了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……蕾拉小姐你也能看見了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.75,0:02:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.67,0:02:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫魯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.14,0:02:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫魯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.58,0:02:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫夫魯 舞臺的精靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.08,0:02:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是蕾拉小姐 夠冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.55,0:03:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不像是我的腦子有問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得有問題的是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.29,0:03:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.01,0:03:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，蕾拉小姐以前是看不見的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉現在已經被舞臺選中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.27,0:03:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是她能夠挑戰夢幻的超絕技的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻的超絕技？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.64,0:03:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經有人挑戰過一次，之後就再也沒有成功過的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.21,0:03:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的人過於害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的人勉強挑戰而喪失性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.86,0:03:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要挑戰的話，需要卡萊多劇團的二人組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.21,0:03:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人組？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.69,0:03:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑戰夢幻的超絕技需要二位元明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前失敗的那二個人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.28,0:03:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.27,0:04:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們對我隱瞞了其中一個人看不見我的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假裝能夠看見我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是蕾拉小姐能看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.59,0:04:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我們吧  夫魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻的超絕技到底是什麼樣的絕技？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不能告訴你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.48,0:04:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須等到你們二人都具備那個資格時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.85,0:04:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資格？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.79,0:04:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要等到什麼時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼才能具備那個資格？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.71,0:04:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就是明天 或許是10年以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.51,0:04:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了吧 現在就告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你現在就挑戰這個絕技的話……	
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.07,0:04:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼想都只有死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.52,0:05:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我覺得和蕾拉小姐一起就可以成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.47,0:05:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.07,0:05:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐 我會努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.53,0:05:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意和我一起嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具明星真的是蕾拉小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.95,0:05:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算上時差乘最早的班機到倫敦的確能夠擠出時間的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.45,0:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想和蕾拉小姐一起挑戰夢幻的超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.39,0:05:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻的超絕技？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.01,0:05:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.26,0:05:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我自己也不是很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我覺得不論是什麼絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.69,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和蕾拉小姐一起就一定能夠成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 看吧 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史上最精彩的表演即將開始的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.12,0:06:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COME ON  COME ON  
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.87,0:06:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說了嗎 面具明星居然是蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.69,0:06:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也聽說了的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.08,0:06:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白了自己還是想和蕾拉小姐一起演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.45,0:06:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發覺的太遲了的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也是這感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.76,0:06:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在客人這麼少也是因為蕾拉小姐不在這裏吧 一定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意的話就走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們被解雇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.33,0:06:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.25,0:06:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個卡萊多劇團的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.57,0:06:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不止呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.58,0:06:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女的是……蕾拉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你不會來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影的拍攝怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.75,0:06:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.05,0:07:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你找我有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能回來 蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.72,0:07:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想和你同台演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你才是我的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.54,0:07:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我的搭檔是空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.40,0:07:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能會和空一起挑戰夢幻的超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.87,0:07:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和空一起挑戰夢幻的超絕技？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.74,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.44,0:07:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要挑戰的話也該是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.33,0:07:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.89,0:08:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看卡萊多劇團的表演時真的以為那是夢境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾渴望能夠站在這個舞臺上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學第一次上體操課時特別開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.03,0:08:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候第一次知道得到掌聲的時候的感覺真的很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天拼命的練習原本完不成的技藝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.36,0:08:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦完成並獲得掌聲時會高興的不由自已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.15,0:08:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次在舞臺上獲得掌聲時真的很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.98,0:08:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以更精彩的絕技……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.15,0:08:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加精彩的表演……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想獻給觀眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.09,0:08:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.95,0:08:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和蕾拉小姐一起……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.33,0:09:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻的超絕技？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得卡洛斯應該知道些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.13,0:09:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有人挑戰過的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.71,0:09:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，但是他會不會說就不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止還沒和人說過話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.51,0:09:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑戰的人是我和空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.65,0:09:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們二個的話應該沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告訴你卡洛斯的聯絡方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！糟了 忘了看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.65,0:09:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅 拜託再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下啊 蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.46,0:09:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空每天都這麼努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.78,0:09:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之在蕾拉小姐承認我這個搭檔前只有努力練習了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.84,0:09:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 這個是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.55,0:09:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.39,0:10:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉•哈姆雷特和苗木野空將在原卡萊多劇團\N以性命相搏挑戰夢幻的超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.59,0:10:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是下個月哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.98,0:10:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.71,0:10:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.83,0:10:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問卡萊多劇團是不是公佈了 將表演夢幻的超絕技的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門票已經賣完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.24,0:10:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這個節目的演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.61,0:10:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.19,0:10:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.31,0:10:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門票已經都賣完了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.79,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想要的話可以給你貴賓席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你告訴我人數，立刻就……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.54,0:10:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道夢幻的超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.01,0:10:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.50,0:10:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說蕾拉小姐答應挑戰夢幻的超絕技了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由利擅自做主公佈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.02,0:10:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想看我們的笑話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.58,0:11:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是很敬佩挑戰這麼困難的絕技的你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.59,0:11:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借個舞臺給你們而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.93,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想逃避的話就趁現在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.49,0:11:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候都可以放棄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.91,0:11:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正賣出去的門票是不會退還的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.84,0:11:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會取消的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.12,0:11:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們也有個條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.23,0:11:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.40,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要夢幻的超絕技能夠完成就把卡萊多劇團還給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.16,0:11:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊 我期待你們的絕技能夠平安完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.70,0:11:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下定決心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空，無論發生什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.71,0:11:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要和你完成夢幻的超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.23,0:12:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還要在這個舞臺上表演給觀眾看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.40,0:12:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.65,0:12:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們還不知道那是個怎麼樣的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼練習呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.06,0:12:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯知道練習方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.23,0:12:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看過從前那二個人的練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.75,0:12:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說如果真的想挑戰的話就來布蘭德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那裏特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.82,0:12:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會去吧 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.52,0:12:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.53,0:12:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的說會把卡萊多劇團還給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，為了大家一定要完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回我們的卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆的主意啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.15,0:12:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.67,0:12:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 喬納森也為空加加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去看表演吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經通過電話預定了票子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.94,0:12:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以訓練員的身份參加特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.95,0:13:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.62,0:13:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.60,0:13:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.83,0:13:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.81,0:13:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆知道夢幻的超絕技到底是什麼樣的絕技麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.11,0:13:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記了，如果沒有那個資格就是死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.03,0:13:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.70,0:13:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是很危險吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會幫助你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該高興的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.29,0:13:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 我雖然會全力支持你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.92,0:13:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.22,0:13:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果夢幻的超絕技真的是很危險的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會阻止你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.25,0:14:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.40,0:14:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.73,0:14:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.75,0:14:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.03,0:14:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.69,0:14:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好思想準備了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是有不好的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.40,0:14:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發MAIL問了以前卡萊多劇團的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.35,0:14:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前有人挑戰過夢幻的超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.29,0:14:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說那個人死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說那個人就是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想下一個做這個的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.11,0:15:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我嘗嘗這個味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太好吃的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你來幫忙做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.17,0:15:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經聲援你了的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完之後再做100次單手俯臥撐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.67,0:15:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.53,0:16:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.16,0:16:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天就到這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.93,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空要右手舉杠鈴100次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.63,0:16:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.49,0:17:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你切吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.51,0:17:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 不過沒關係的，我自己來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.86,0:17:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.39,0:17:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.28,0:17:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說真能夠完成那種演技？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.36,0:17:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說過如果要完成這個絕技必須有絕對的自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.32,0:17:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.34,0:17:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種自信不僅僅是對她們本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是對我們這些站在周圍的人說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果對蕾拉和空有信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要直到最後她們看到的都是不安的神情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.22,0:17:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果對她們沒有信心的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.07,0:17:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如現在立刻就離開這裏，別妨礙她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.81,0:17:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有不要對空說夢幻的超絕技到底是什麼樣的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.32,0:18:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有那個資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.95,0:18:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過得忍著點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.38,0:18:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸疼的地方一定要揉開才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要練習空中投球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有後天是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.14,0:18:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.74,0:18:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.73,0:18:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我能撐到這次特訓結束麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.59,0:18:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的表演夢幻的超絕技麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空開始不安了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.90,0:18:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.46,0:18:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經一周了，都只是在練習這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.48,0:18:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要發牢騷，快點練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.04,0:19:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼好像突然變了個人似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別撒嬌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.40,0:19:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是要表演夢幻的超絕技的可是你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.02,0:19:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉第一階段練習結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始練習使用鋼繩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.63,0:19:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 你跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.13,0:19:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.55,0:19:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鐵球大致和蕾拉的體重相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須只用右手就要擋住它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.65,0:19:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果做不到這點就不能成為蕾拉的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.77,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以，我盡力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.01,0:19:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果對蕾拉和空有信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.15,0:19:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要直到最後她們看到的都是不安的神情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.77,0:19:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.66,0:19:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個特訓請讓我來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.25,0:20:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.52,0:20:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.70,0:20:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.61,0:20:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.40,0:20:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.66,0:20:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.67,0:20:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.94,0:20:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.76,0:20:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.81,0:20:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.48,0:20:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.14,0:21:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.80,0:21:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定……一定要和蕾拉小姐一起完成夢幻的超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.09,0:21:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.43,0:21:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到這點，你是不可能完成夢幻的超絕技的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.18,0:21:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻的超絕技到底是什麼樣的絕技呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.38,0:21:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連夢幻的超絕技到底是什麼樣的絕技都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.54,0:21:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能努力到最後嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫魯！夫魯你在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫魯 告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.75,0:21:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.14,0:21:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.02,0:22:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前已經說了必須等到你們都具有挑戰的資格時才能告訴你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.87,0:22:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行嗎？嗎？嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.16,0:22:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告 卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.75,0:22:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有自信說“我就是蕾拉的搭檔”嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.31,0:22:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是超級特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.12,0:22:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.77,0:22:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空會累壞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.24,0:22:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能轉移視線，不想放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.39,0:22:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想認輸了，想逃避了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.23,0:22:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐對我說些什麼吧！吧！吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.35,0:22:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.26,0:22:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀是夢想，飛向空
